<plot>Wes, Vern and Indian Joe are three cowhands on the way to a cattle drive. Coming upon what is to be an omen of their future...outlaws hung by a group of vigilantes...the trio finds shelter at a cabin, only to discover that their "hosts" are men who have robbed a stagecoach and killed the driver. When an avenging posse attacks the cabin, Wes and Vern escape, only to find that they have become branded as 'outlaws' by the posse, who relentlessly pursue them.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?463087</url></doc>
